# Place Indian legal act PDF files here before running seed_chroma.py
#
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT: Use the NEW criminal codes (effective 1 July 2024).
#     The IPC and CrPC have been replaced. Download from indiacode.nic.in
#
# Required PDF files:
#
#   bns.pdf
#     → Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita (BNS), 2023
#     → REPLACES Indian Penal Code (IPC), 1860
#     → https://indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/20062
#
#   bnss.pdf
#     → Bharatiya Nagarik Suraksha Sanhita (BNSS), 2023
#     → REPLACES Code of Criminal Procedure (CrPC), 1973
#     → https://indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/20062
#
#   bsa.pdf
#     → Bharatiya Sakshya Adhiniyam (BSA), 2023
#     → REPLACES Indian Evidence Act, 1872
#     → https://indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/20062
#
#   consumer_protection_act.pdf
#     → Consumer Protection Act, 2019 (UNCHANGED)
#     → https://indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/14784
#
#   negotiable_instruments_act.pdf
#     → Negotiable Instruments Act, 1881 — Section 138 (UNCHANGED)
#     → https://indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1420
#
#   transfer_of_property_act.pdf
#     → Transfer of Property Act, 1882 (UNCHANGED)
#     → https://indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1396
#
#   rent_control_act.pdf
#     → Delhi Rent Control Act, 1958 (state-level, UNCHANGED)
#     → https://delhigovt.nic.in
#
# NOTE: seed_chroma.py supports both .pdf and .txt formats.
#       Digital PDFs (text-selectable) work best — scanned PDFs may yield garbled text.
#       Do NOT place IPC or CrPC files here; those laws are superseded.
